narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: yes, you learn SO much about the chinese economy and future growth potential.
Certainly! A good primer on the Chinese economy.

The class was a classic lecture, with the Prof talking to students. However, we broke into groups each class and discussed questions on the ppts. Overall, the material was interesting, but the pace was a bit slow (to cater to the English language abilities of the PKU students).
